##Overview
A simple e-commerce website to showcase products with the ability to add items to the shopping cart.
##Features
User authentication (login / register)
Product listing page
Product details page
Shopping cart (Add / Remove items)
Calculate total price
Secure online payment (future integration with PayPal / Visa / MasterCard)

##Tech Stack
HTML, CSS, JavaScript
Tailwind CSS
Flowbite
Toaster (notifications)
FontAwesome (icons)
framework (Angular)

##Installation
git clone https://github.com/menna-saed/E-commerce.git
cd E-commerce
npm install
npm start

